name: Hinecatone 1 of 15. Ultra rare
bio: Kia ora! Call me Hinecatone 1 of 15. Ultra rare. Ahhh, is there anything more beautiful than the blossoming of a new friendship? Spring is a time of change and renewal, so I’m looking to branch out. I’ve got to find some new homes for my plant buddies—do you have a good pot dealer?
